      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 represents the pinnacle of the E46 chassis, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a comprehensive service history that includes preventative rod bearing replacement, a complete VANOS overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure peak structural integrity. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, while the variable M-differential delivers precise torque distribution. Every bushing, damper, and factory seal remains in showroom condition, preserving the car's celebrated handling geometry and analog feedback. Finished in Titanium Silver over an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this is a turn-key collector's piece with zero deferred maintenance.",
