    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures it remains free of swirl marks, stone chips, or scratches. Every panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are pristine, showing no signs of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. All technology interfaces and buttons function with tactile precision, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively at authorized service centers\u2014full records are included. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
